{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"51617f318f","title":"对曾志等要求给陶铸甄别的来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da660985e2","index":0,"year":1975,"month":10,"day":30,"articleId":"51617f318f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"1624a49727","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"原中共中央政治局常委、中央书记处常务书记、国务院副总理陶铸的妻子曾志、女儿陶斯亮1975年10月分别给毛泽东写信，反映陶铸生前对个人历史问题的态度，对专案组关于陶铸所谓历史问题的结论提出质疑，希望能换一些同志对陶铸进行甄别工作，并在中央讨论、主席审批前将历史结论向家属说明。中共中央办公厅将这两封来信和毛泽东的批语一起作为1975年第二六二号文件印发中央政治局。1978年12月，中共十一届三中全会审查和纠正了过去对陶铸的错误结论，肯定了他对党和人民的贡献，使他的宽案得到平反。"},{"id":"c33f400d9c","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"汪东兴，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c5e7ff6ffb","type":"title","text":"对曾志等要求给陶铸甄别的来信的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f"},{"id":"1624a49727","type":"paragraph","text":"印发在京政治局同志请注东兴时同志的处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f"},{"id":"c33f400d9c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f"},{"id":"1d2f08a122","type":"paragraph","text":"十月三十日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f"}],"page":{"id":"fc079ca4ba","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"51617f318f","start":85,"end":85}}}},"__N_SSG":true}